data.description: This charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath residence offers a delightful living experience. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated kitchen and fresh flooring in the kitchen and dining room. The upstairs boasts new windows that flood the space with natural light. The thoughtfully designed floor plan features a spacious living room complete with a cozy woodstove, a remodeled kitchen, a dining area, three bedrooms, and a full bath. The full, unfinished basement presents a world of possibilities, as it can be easily transformed into additional living space. Laundry hookups are already in place, and it's pre-plumbed for a bathroom, making customization a breeze. Step outside to enjoy a small deck with a view of the neighborhood and a generous fenced backyard. You'll love the covered deck, perfect for outdoor relaxation. Additional features include a handy storage shed and mature landscaping that adds a touch of nature's beauty to your surroundings. This home's location is a true gem, nestled in the heart of a fantastic neighborhood. It's conveniently close to Logan Health, FVCC, and an abundance of shopping and dining options. This property combines comfort, style, and convenience to create the perfect place to call home.
